1.0.name: wordpress/issuu-pdf-sync
1.0.description: Allow to create PDF Flipbooks with the http://issuu.com service. You just need to get a free key and all your PDF will synchronised on the site. Then you'll be abble to insert flipbooks inside your post without having to quit the WordPress admin pannel.
